    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Members of a people or group who have no permanent residence or settlement but move about in regular seasonal or cyclical routes to obtain sustenance.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
